overview.en: The Ultimate Project for Vehicle Energy Conservation and Environmental Protection Shapes the Value Chain and Influence Center of Energy Conservation and Environmental Protection. Based on proprietary automotive energy-saving and environment-friendly fuels. The automobile market in China is over 800 million private cars amd growing. The new retail of the aftermarket vehicles is the ultimate application value.
overview.zh: 创建节能环保的价值链产业平台，塑造节能环保的影响力中心，以自有专利的汽车节能环保爆品为核心，快速占领中国8亿私家车大货车汽车市场，以创建汽车后市场区块链新零售为终极应用价值。
